{"tid":2430382,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"菁蒼真經- 轉至大道無門","createTime":"2021-03-03T01:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T03:27:36.000Z","uid":188322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"628abf1864f28c071ffbe6926c8152592b31c274","tid":2430382,"uid":188322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"菁蒼真經<br />\n<br />\n炒之道，損有餘而贏不足，是故虛勝實，不足勝有餘。其意博，其理奧，其趣深，天地之股價，陰陽之燭線，變化之圖表，死生之倉位，不動如五嶽泰山之穩，出手若雷霆霹靂之勢，稽其態有微，驗之事有思，誠可謂至道之宗，奉生之始矣。假若天機迅發，妙識玄通，開倉雖屬乎時機，滿倉亦資於膽量，惜只買而不沽，贏在賬目浮雲矣。然刻意研精，探微索隱，或洞察轉角，則高位盡清，故動則有成，猶鬼神幽讚，而命世奇傑，時時間出焉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n菁蒼教義<br />\n含世間之炒股真理<br />\n<br />\n全悟之足以富可敵國<br />\n半悟之足以不愁吃喝<br />\n不悟之半生浮沉於市<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc5b03a7607dd5dda09f2176a0021df6a4aa7cf","tid":2430382,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"好酒好酒"},{"pid":"f5637abb3a3d3465a3b183e6684b87aea2e811fd","tid":2430382,"uid":188322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbc5b03a7607dd5dda09f2176a0021df6a4aa7cf","tid":2430382,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"好酒好酒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"笑盡牛市股神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acf9da0458f700e85406e4e3782d124db508abe","tid":2430382,"uid":188322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3721194b8b0fc2fa7e2e335abaffd8e8f9ade4ff","tid":2430382,"uid":188322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}